    "4975090277_COAP协议持续GET操作时模组死机": {
      "title": "COAP协议持续GET操作时模组死机",
      "file": "COAP协议持续GET操作时模组死机.md",
      "hash": "6a807d9922b51319d2f0cbb85db1c7ee",
      "archived_at": "2026-06-12T15:17:48.510622",
      "source_files": [
        "Bug分析.md"
      ],
      "summary": {
        "platform": "EC626",
        "module": "CoAP/libcoap/堆内存",
        "bug_type": "资源耗尽",
        "symptoms": [
          "COAP死机",
          "堆内存泄漏",
          "OPTLIST泄漏",
          "LL_SORT bug",
          "pvPortMallocEC返回NULL",
          "ASSERT死机",
          "COAPCLOSE循环",
          "内存持续下降"
        ],
        "root_cause": "COAP客户端在COAPCLOSE→COAPOPEN循环中存在heap内存泄漏，OPTLIST（t=12）100%泄漏率（120 allocs / 0 frees）。根因是coap_add_optlist_pdu()中的LL_SORT宏在ICCARM编译器NO_DECLTYPE模式下，将*options置为NULL后无法正确恢复，导致6个optlist节点（~143B/周期）全部泄漏，最终堆内存耗尽触发ASSERT死机",
        "call_chain_summary": "COAPSEND → coap_new_request → coap_add_optlist_pdu → LL_SORT((*options), order_opts) → *options=NULL → OPTLIST泄漏 → 堆耗尽 → coapSlpDeInit → coap_recv_task_Init → xTaskCreate → pvPortMallocEC(1575) → NULL → ASSERT死机",
        "keywords": [
          "COAP死机",
          "OPTLIST泄漏",
          "LL_SORT",
          "NO_DECLTYPE",
          "ICCARM",
          "utlist",
          "coap_add_optlist_pdu",
          "堆内存泄漏",
          "pvPortMallocEC NULL",
          "EC626 COAP",
          "CoAP close循环",
          "内存耗尽死机"
        ]
      }
    },
